node.text: Zianna Oliphant at only 9 years old is speaking for the ENTIRE black community with GRACE, FACTS, and HEART. The blatant disrespect and flat out violence being demonstrated towards black people and everyone else taking a stand out there shows how broken our system actually is. God bless this young lady. Having MANY years over someone doesn’t undoubtedly speak truth. If you’re an adult and you still carry hate and stand against the rights of ANY families for their race it shows that LIFE AND HARMONY is above all. We can make a difference and we will. ❤️#BLACKLIVESMATTER
